\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93What is it?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93This is what is left of the world\u8217\'92s story. Solraheen planted all these lines of fate, and once, when the world was young, they were each drawn across the world and into the future. Then battles, and now the story is shredded. I\u8217\'92ve shorn my fair share of them. I\u8217\'92ve rewoven some, too. But I am the last good woman who can.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93The difference between fate and will is semantic. You have the one world line. If that line runs out because . If it has been manipulated, it is called fate.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93I don\u8217\'92t have one.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Yes. You\u8217\'92ve been inviscerated with Black. It suppresses your Spark\u8217\'92s expression. Don\u8217\'92t ever let evil tell you that the bottom inside is empty. If it was, they wouldn\u8217\'92t have needed to fill you with Black.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93The mission is to get it out of you.\u8221\'94\line \u8220\'93How?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93It will be difficult. Only you can do it. Your Spark has to push it out. Your will must become so great, that .\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 You\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92ve never seen the fruits of this world. Let me show you.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 ---elrahet. he has a sparl inside all that black.if it were true that creation had no purpose, why would they need to fill you with black?}
