\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Been fighting so long to hold things together. I\u8217\'92m tired. I cannot do this forever. This is my plan. Have faith that the future will end up how it will be. }
