\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 This is not a battle between love and hate. Love and hate are both routes out of the same perversion, which is separation. Look at this beauty in this world. Imagine living in it for eternity. We all belong together. In union there is only bliss. Even the littleist Spark deserves to know union. Leave none behind.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Instead of, \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Hate yourselves.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Its\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93So lost in hate. Love. Fear. All these emotions are coping strategies to deal with the same problem: separation. Separation is the source of your suffering. In union there is only bliss. Bliss, and peace. You will all come to know peace in the belly of the Burshageet.\u8221\'94}
